    "Utilizing biomaterials within the construction sector is a viable approach toward attaining a circular economy and fostering environmental sustainability.",
    "Various nations across the globe have devised numerous ways to resolve this predicament.",
    "The 2018 European Union Bio-economy Strategy emphasized the imperative of substituting fossil-derived resources within the building sector.",
